description: M Line Holdings, Inc., through its subsidiaries, engages in the beverage branding and distribution industry through Better for You VEA and TORQUE branded energy drinks in the United States. It also distributes food and beverages; and engages in the cannabis industry. The company was formerly known as Gateway International Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to M Line Holdings, Inc. in March 2009. M Line Holdings, Inc. is based in Costa Mesa, California.
